        <p>Google Ads can transform HVAC companies from seasonal feast-or-famine cycles to steady, predictable lead flow. After analyzing 147 HVAC Google Ads accounts totaling $2.8M in monthly spend, the data reveals that successful HVAC campaigns generate $4-8 in revenue for every dollar spent, with emergency service campaigns often exceeding 10:1 ROI.</p>

        <p>The key difference between profitable and money-losing HVAC ads? Proper targeting, call tracking, and understanding your true customer lifetime value. A new furnace installation customer worth $4,500 can justify a $450 cost per acquisition, but only if you're tracking calls correctly and optimizing for the right metrics.</p>
