      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <p>Advanced call tracking setups use different phone numbers for emergency repair versus installation campaigns. This allows precise ROI calculation by service type and helps optimize budget allocation between emergency and planned work.</p>

        <p>Call scoring systems rate lead quality based on call duration, appointment booking, and service type requested. Emergency repair calls under 2 minutes rarely convert, while installation calls over 8 minutes convert at 67% rates.</p>
